文 |《财经》数据研究员 徐进图 |《财经》视觉中心编辑 |谢丽容1.全国累计确诊病例趋势截至2月15日24:00，全国累计报告确诊新冠肺炎病例68500人。
At 24: 00 on February 15, a cumulative total of 68,500 new cases of newly diagnosed pneumonia nationwide were reported. & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45;
以下分地区情况。
The situation in the following subregions.
图1有朋友提醒小编：你不要盲目乐观，要知道R0值可是2-3，甚至5！小编问：所以呢？答曰：那意味着一个病人一天可以传染2-5人，太厉害了！想起印度国王和宰相下棋的故事了吧？让我们算算有多厉害。
It means that a patient can infect 2-5 people a day, that's too bad! Remember the story of the Indian king and prime minister playing chess? Let's calculate how bad it is.
姑且按最低的2说，一天一人传两个，第二天就传四个……依次类推然后求和（指数数列求和公式）。
Let's just say the lowest two, pass two a day, pass four the next... and then generalize by analogy (sum of exponential series).
如果从湖北那老两口和儿子12月23日开始咳嗽算起，到1月23日武汉封城，总的传染人数=3X2^-1=12884901887人。
If from Hubei old couple and son December 23 start coughing, January 23, Wuhan closed the city, the total number of infected persons = 3X2 ^-1 = 12884901887.
128.8亿！如果这是真的，我们还用紧张吗？早在大年三十，要么就是全世界所有人都已不在，要么就是所有活着的都被传染了两遍，怕是早都有抗体了吧。
If it's true, are we nervous? As early as the New Year's Eve, either everyone else in the world is gone, or everyone alive has been infected twice, probably with antibodies.
小编不是学传染病学的，今天暂不讨论R0。
I'm not studying infectious diseases. I'm not talking about R0 today.
只想先提醒一下，科学论断往往有前提假设。
Just want to remind first, scientific judgment often has premise hypothesis.
R0是在假定没有外界干预、交流无障碍而所有人又同样容易被感染的前提下得出的理论值。
R0 is a theoretical value based on the assumption that there is no outside intervention, communication is accessible and all people are equally vulnerable to infection.
真实世界中这种前提从来没有存在过。
This premise has never existed in the real world.
所以真实R一般总会比R0低。
So real R is generally always lower than R0.
比如这次，1月23日之前我们至少还有医院，之后又有封城等包括追踪、隔离、大家戴口罩。
This time, for example, we had hospitals at least until January 23, followed by cordon-and-seek, quarantining, and masks.
真实R值会不断与R0拉开差距。
The true R value will continue to widen the gap with R0.
所以对科学结论不能简单地“不明觉厉”，更不要过度地“细思恐极”。
Therefore, the scientific conclusion can not simply "unconsciously", not to mention excessive "think about the fear of pole."
小编不预先选择悲观乐观，只是要看统计数字，相信真像藏在数据中，终究可以挖出来。
Small editor does not pre-select pessimistic optimism, just to see statistics, believe that the truth hidden in the data, after all can be dug out.
回到（图1），怎么看？累计数据往往能反映趋势。
Back (Figure 1), what do you think? Aggregate data tend to reflect trends.
由图可见，1）尽管早期确有指数函数R值大于1的特征，大约在2月初就已经改变了性质，曲线由下凸改为上凸，完全看不出R值大于1了。
As can be seen from the diagram, 1) Although the early exponent function did have an R value greater than 1, the nature had changed around the beginning of February, with the curve changing from lower convex to upward convex, with no R value greater than 1.
还记得前面的“数说”说过“数学拐点在山腰”吗？可以合理推测在这一阶段两个特点：1)由于各项防控措施开始见效，实际R值已经从大于1切换成小于1了。
At the end of the paragraph, you will be given 10 seconds to write a composition on the topic Is the point of math inflection at the mountainside It is reasonable to assume that at this stage two characteristics: 1) The actual R value has changed from more than 1 to less than 1 as control measures begin to take effect.
2)国内非湖北地区和湖北非武汉地区的趋势曲线都已渐渐趋于平缓，见顶的迹象十分明显。
2) The trend curves of non-Hubei and Hubei non-Wuhan areas in China have gradually levelled off and the signs of peaking are very clear.
2. 新增病例：国内非湖北地区继续坚定下降，有望近日归零图 2国内非湖北新增病例下降至200人以内，我们推测本月20日前可以归零或基本归零。
2. New cases: China's non-Hubei region continues to decline resolutely, and it is expected that the number of new cases in non-Hubei will fall to 200 in recent days.
有很多网友担心这样的预测是否过于乐观，我们明天解释。
Many netizens are worried that such a forecast is too optimistic, we will explain tomorrow.
图 3今天数据可以判定，湖北非武汉地区数据可以判定已消化完“堰塞湖”，重新走上每日新增病例下降的通道。
Fig. 3 Today's data can determine that Hubei non-Wuhan region data can be judged to have digested "Yan Sehu," a daily decline in the number of new cases of the channel.
图 4武汉数据看上去也很不错，按新口径连续两天下降。
Figure 4 Wuhan data also looks good, according to the new calibres fell for two consecutive days.
3. 确诊病例增速：湖北非武汉地区继续降至接近2%，是个惊喜！国内非湖北地区增速继续下降至2%以下，大概率在2月20日前后归零图5昨天按老口径计算湖北非武汉地区的病例增速降至接近2%，小编是不敢信的，也没有采纳。
The rate of increase of confirmed cases continues to drop to nearly 2% in non-Wuhan areas of Hubei Province, a pleasant surprise. The growth rate of cases in non-Wuhan areas of Hubei province continued to drop to less than 2%.
但今天新口径还是给出了这个惊喜。
But today the new caliber still gives the surprise.
为湖北点赞！武汉新口径增速回落到4%附近，趋于健康。
For Hubei praise! Wuhan new caliber growth rate fell to 4% near, tend to be healthy.
国内非湖北地区增速降至2%以内，有望率先归零。
Domestic non-Hubei growth rate fell to less than 2%, is expected to lead to zero.
4.国内非湖北地区追踪力度加大，存量继续下降图 6湖北虽只是微弱回升却能表现出其对密切接触者追踪力度的提高。
The domestic non-Hubei area tracking intensity increases, the stock continues to decline Figure 6 Hubei although only a slight recovery can show its close contacts to improve the tracking efforts.
这对进一步控制疫情十分重要！国内非湖北地区对密切接触者追踪力度仍在加大。
This is very important to further control the epidemic! Close contacts in non-Hubei areas of China are still increasing.
图 7此时湖北这一存量数据出现下降应该表明疫情减缓。
Fig. 7 The decline in Hubei stock data at this time should indicate a slowdown in the outbreak.
国内非湖北地区继续下降降幅加大。
The decline in non-Hubei areas continued to increase.
5.疑似病例新增和存量双下滑图8湖北和非湖北地区都出现明显下降。
The increase of suspected cases and the decrease of the stock showed a significant decrease in Hubei and non-Hubei areas.
图9湖北和国内非湖北地区下降。
Fig. 9 Falling of Hubei and non-Hubei areas.
6.国内非湖北地区在院治疗人数见顶图10湖北在院治疗人数仍上升，国内非湖北地区减幅加大。
The number of people treated in hospitals in non-Hubei areas in China is still on the rise in Hubei and the decrease in non-Hubei areas in China is increasing.
7.新增治愈和病死率图11每日新增治愈国内非湖北、湖北非武汉地区继续上升。
New Healing and Death Rate Figure 11 The number of new cures per day continued to rise in non-Hubei and Hubei non-Wuhan areas.
武汉回调。
Wuhan callback.
图12国内非湖北地区新增治愈与新增确诊人数已于2月12日成功越过“黄金交叉”点。
Fig. 12 The number of newly diagnosed and cured cases in non-Hubei areas of China successfully crossed the Golden Cross on February 12.
意味着从这一天起，若不出意外，国内非湖北地区近10000例在院治疗者将开始逐步减少。
This means that from this day, if no accident, the nearly 10,000 patients in non-Hubei region of China will start to gradually reduce.
在此之前，国内非湖北地区的另外两个重要存量“尚在接受医学观察人数”和“待排查疑似病例”皆已先后见顶下降。
Before that, the other two important stocks in non-Hubei areas of China "are still under medical observation" and "pending investigation of suspected cases" have all peaked.
由于这三大存量（我们在数说疫情0211曾有阐述）都对应着巨大医疗资源和社会资源，它们的全面见顶下降，毫无疑问是关乎整个战局态势的“关键拐点”！图13（湖北非武汉地区新增确诊和新增治愈人数）湖北非武汉地区该数据也出现“黄金交叉”，可视为湖北非武汉地区的“关键拐点”，这一点的到来只比国内非湖北地区晚三天。
The overall decline of these three stocks, which we have described in case 0211, corresponds to huge medical and social resources, is undoubtedly the "key inflection point" of the whole situation! Figure 13 shows the "golden cross" in the non-Wuhan area of Hubei Province.
图14病死率缓慢提升，总体态势正常。
Figure 14. Slow increase in fatality rate and normal overall situation.
疫情暴发初期，每日新增病例猛增，有可能快过病死人数增长，因而导致病死率下降。
In the early stages of the outbreak, the number of new cases per day surged, potentially increasing faster than the number of deaths, leading to a decline in the fatality rate.
经过一段时间滞后，随病程进展会带来死亡人数增加较快；与此同时，随着疫情得到控制，每日新增确诊病例出现明显下降，累计确诊病例增速放缓。
Over time, the progression of the disease leads to a faster increase in the number of deaths; at the same time, as the epidemic is brought under control, there is a marked decrease in the number of new confirmed cases per day and a slowing in the cumulative rate of confirmed cases.
这一快（分子），一慢（分母），会导致病死率缓慢回升。
This fast (molecular), a slow (denominator), will lead to a slow recovery in the death rate.
只有在疫情基本结束时，这个数值才会逼近“最终病死率”。
Only when the epidemic is largely over will this figure approach the "final fatality rate."
小结：湖北进一步化解“堰塞湖”，非武汉地区迅速重回下降轨道，武汉显现平稳态势。
Summary: Hubei further defused "Yan Sehu," non-Wuhan region quickly returned to the downward trajectory, Wuhan appears to be stable situation.
湖北非武汉地区越过抗疫战局“关键拐点”，可望由战略防守转为战略反攻。
Hubei non-Wuhan region crossed the "key inflection point" of the battle against the epidemic and is expected to shift from strategic defense to strategic counterattack.
国内非湖北地区新增病例有望在2月20日前基本归零，也就是大家所期盼累计确诊病例见“顶”。
New cases in non-Hubei areas of China are expected to reach zero by February 20, which means that the cumulative number of confirmed cases is expected to "peak."
